data.description: Country living with just enough land to enjoy every bit of peace and quiet. From the rocking chair front porch to the back deck looking over your fire pit and easy to maintain 4 acre plot.  This charming three bed two full bath home is just the right size for your family and friends. You can keep everything you want in the full unfinished basement it even has a wood burning stove. Easy access to Hwy 111  and just 35 minutes to Downtown Chattanooga. Seller uses Dish for TV and Bledsoe Fiber for high-speed internet. Seller will remove barn, coop and fence if buyer desires, property is for sale as is.
